title: Mr Del Discography 1999-2013 (12 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
MR DEL DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 12 releases...

 * 1999 - Lyrical Millenium
 * 2000 - 2nd Coming
 * 2000 - Enter The Light
 * 2003 - Church Age
 * 2003 - Da Takeover
 * 2005 - The Future
 * 2006 - Memphis To ATL
 * 2007 - Crunk Soul
 * 2007 - Hope Dealer
 * 2009 - Thrilla
 * 2010 - Tennman
 * 2013 - Sunglasses - Single

Mr Del is an American Christian hip-hop artist and music producer. He began his music career recording a song with the rap group Three 6 Mafia. After dedicating his life to Christ in 2000, he left the secular rap genre to begin his own ministry and record label.

For Him,
TorrentTracts - December 2013
